#: app/templates/privacy.html:29
msgid "How Your Data Is Used"
msgstr "Mar a thathas a' cleachdadh an dàta agad"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:31
msgid ""
"Your data is used solely for the purpose of delivering reminders and "
"messages according to your preferences."
msgstr ""
"Tha an dàta agad air a chleachdadh dìreach airson lìbhrigeadh chuimhneachain"
" is theachdaireachdan a rèir do roghainnean."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:32
msgid ""
"Grylli does not share, sell, or transmit your personal data to any third "
"parties."
msgstr ""
"Chan eil Grylli a’ roinn, a’ reic, no a’ cur an dàta pearsanta agad gu treas"
" phàrtaidhean sam bith."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:36
msgid ""
"Sensitive fields like passwords and tokens are only stored if you provide "
"them explicitly. Existing values are never exposed unless you choose to "
"reveal them."
msgstr ""
"Chan eil raointean mothachail leithid faclan-faire agus tòcanan air an "
"stòradh ach ma bheir thu iad gu soilleir. Chan eil luachan a tha ann mu "
"thràth air am foillseachadh mura tagh thu an fhoillseachadh."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:38
msgid "Grylli contains no external analytics, telemetry, or tracking scripts."
msgstr ""
"Chan eil dad a-muigh an sin taobh a-muigh anailis, telemetry no "
"sgriobtaichean lorg."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:41
msgid "Your Rights"
msgstr "Na Còraichean agad"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:43
msgid ""
"You can export all of your data at any time from the Account Settings page."
msgstr ""
"Faodaidh tu d’ uile dàta às-mhalairt uair sam bith bhon duilleag Roghainnean"
" Cunntais."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:44
msgid "You may permanently delete your account and all associated data."
msgstr ""
"Chan urrainn dhut do chunntas a sguabadh às oir is tusa am fear rianachd mu "
"dheireadh."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:45
msgid ""
"If you are using a self-hosted instance, contact the instance administrator "
"for data inquiries."
msgstr ""
"Ma tha thu a’ cleachdadh foillseachadh fhèin, cuir fios chun neach-rianachd "
"foillseachaidh airson ceistean dàta."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:48
msgid "Self-Hosting Responsibility"
msgstr "Uallach Fèin-aoigheachd"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:50
msgid ""
"When you self-host Grylli, you are responsible for ensuring all user data is"
" stored and processed in compliance with applicable privacy regulations."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a shuidhicheas tu Grylli fhèin, tha thu an urra ris a h-uile dàta "
"neach-cleachdaidh a stòradh agus a làimhseachadh a rèir nan riaghailtean "
"prìobhaideachd iomchaidh."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:54
msgid ""
"This notice was last updated in June 2025 and may evolve to reflect changes "
"in the software or regulatory landscape."
msgstr ""
"Chaidh an rabhadh seo ùrachadh mu dheireadh san Ògmhios 2025 agus dh’ "
"fhaodadh e a thighinn air adhart airson atharrachaidhean ann am bathar-bog "
