"Find untranslated or incomplete entries and add or improve translations."
msgstr ""
"Lorg inntrigidhean nach eil air an eadar-theangachadh no a tha neo-"
"choileanta agus cuir ris no leasaich eadar-theangachaidhean."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:27
msgid "You may use a PO file editor or a text editor."
msgstr "Faodaidh tu editor faidhle PO no editor teacsa a chleachdadh."

#: app/templates/account/translations.html:28
msgid "Copy the file path and the snippet of your changes."
msgstr ""
"Dèan lethbhreac den t-slighe faidhle agus am pìos de na h-atharrachaidhean "
"agad."

